n<br />\n呢期追住黎打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2444f8d5ee76ad61a0334662705288fb46371b","tid":95820,"uid":61279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:39:33.000Z","msg":"休班你真狡猾老是常出現"},{"pid":"2c17a4338c2513be794093de33db78efd61fb09f","tid":95820,"uid":35914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"東方做咩呢排追住班聖人?"},{"pid":"6ae0924d11d7ef55ab1bb4cf1de8270b4a8144e5","tid":95820,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:43:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警犬幾時得罪左百份報<br />\n<br />\n呢期追住黎打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n東方同蘋果都狂咬班警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede9b0282d7d351de3e278a60f70d3922ca89ea4","tid":95820,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>警犬幾時得罪左百份報<br />\n<br />\n呢期追住黎打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n東方同蘋果都狂咬班警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係平時做親新聞都串柒柒，又夾埋記者協會放任警察打記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}